uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.forms.inputs

Class InfoInput

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.forms.inputs.InfoInput
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Input<java.lang.String>, UnmodifiableInput

    public class InfoInput
extends java.lang.Object
implements Input<java.lang.String>, UnmodifiableInput
    Represents an UnmodifiableInput that takes no part in the form validation it just displays informational text. Similar to ConstantInput but cannot cache a value and always validates.
    Author:
    spb
